div.div:
Email Domain
Service: Handles general operations of the domain (controls repository and email library).
Repository: Handles database operations through the required writer, reader and deleter classes.
Entities: The email entity is the subject of all operations inside the email domain.
Collections: Contain and handle a number of entities.
Value Objects: Entity attributes (validate themselves).
Factory: Generates objects that are necessary for the domain
* Argument types and private/protected members are avoided for simplicity.
